What this repository redistributes
========================================================================

1. Original contributions (training, export, deploy, documentation, example-data)
   Copyright (c) 2026 Atharv Sharma
   Licensed under Apache-2.0.

2. NAVSIM-derived packaging and agent integration
   Portions adapt the open NAVSIM / nuPlan planning interfaces. Users must
   obtain full NAVSIM / nuPlan map/sensor data under those projects' licenses
   for training and full evaluation. A one-frame sample for C++ inference is
   included under deploy/example-data/.

3. CUDA-BEVFusion / BEVFusion template
   Camera LSS, BEVPool plugins, and related runtime components follow
   NVIDIA's Apache-2.0 CUDA-BEVFusion / Lidar_AI_Solution materials where
   applicable. The documented LiDAR SCN path does NOT require NVIDIA's
   closed libspconv binary; it executes the exported ONNX SCN graph with
   open-source spconv 2.x (https://github.com/traveller59/spconv).

4. Hydra-MDP / GTRS-style planning decoder
   Trajectory vocabulary scoring and PDM-distillation training follow the
   published Hydra-MDP / GTRS design. Cite those works when using the planner.

